## Title
SitSmart

## Team Members
- Ayanna Garrett
- Logan Castelloe

## Description 
SitSmart is a babysitting app that connects parents to trusted babysitters in the area. Parents search for avaliable sitters, view profiles and reviews, and book a sitter. Babysitters can manage their avaliablity, set their pay rate and list thier skills.

## App Functions
1. Parent (customer role):
    1. Create/modify parent profile - Sign up as a parent.
    2. Find avaliable sitters - Search for sitters by state, city, or reviews
    3. Book a sitter for a specfic date - select from sitter avalibility or request a specific date.
    4. Message the babysitter - private message the sitter in their inbox 
    5. Leave reviews - review sitter on their skills, professionalism, and overall experience.

2. Babysitter (provider role):
    1. Sign up and create their babysitter profile.
    2. Set up on the babysitter search page and set relevant information about themselves (I.e. skills and experience).
    3. Update their proflie and relevant information as needed over time
    4. Respond to contacts and appointments by the parent and coordinate as needed
    5. Reply to reviews from the parents
